data.description: Welcome home! This 2-story residence features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths situated in the established Brighton Village. As soon as you enter you'll feel right at home with so many great features including vaulted ceilings, a beautiful staircase, plenty of natural lighting throughout, newly installed plank flooring & carpet upstairs. Looking for a property at a great price under 300k, with a pool? Look no further the back yard will not disappoint, great for backyard BBQ's and entertaining. Cool down and go for a swim! Great location near park, VMHS and Kaffie Middle School, don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own. This is the home you've been waiting for... See it Today!
